<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You're Invited to CodeStage Assessment</title>
    <!--
    CODESTAGE EMAIL TEMPLATE v1.0

    TEMPLATE VARIABLES TO REPLACE:
    - {{candidateName}} - Candidate's first name or full name
    - {{inviterName}} - Full name of person who sent the invitation
    - {{inviterInitials}} - 1-2 character initials (e.g., "JD" for John Doe)
    - {{assessmentLink}} - Unique time-limited assessment URL
    - {{assessmentNotes}} - Optional notes/instructions from inviter (e.g., meeting link, special instructions)
                            If empty/null, remove the entire "Additional Instructions" section

    CUSTOMIZATION NOTES:
    - All colors use CSS variables for easy theme switching
    - Mobile-responsive design tested on all major email clients
    - Inline styles required for email compatibility
    - Link expiration time can be changed in warning box (currently 10 minutes)

    COLOR PALETTE:
    - Background: #09090b (dark zinc)
    - Card: #18181b (zinc-900)
    - Borders: #27272a (zinc-800)
    - Text primary: #fafafa (zinc-50)
    - Text secondary: #a1a1aa (zinc-400)
    - Text muted: #71717a (zinc-500)
    - Accent: #7c3aed → #a78bfa (purple gradient)
    - CTA: #fafafa on dark background
    - Warning: #fbbf24 (amber-400)
  -->
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #09090b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;">
<!--
  OUTER WRAPPER TABLE
  Note: Uses table-based layout for maximum email client compatibility
-->
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #09090b;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 40px 20px;">
            <!--
              MAIN CONTENT CONTAINER
              Note: max-width keeps email readable on desktop, centered with margin auto
            -->
            <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto;">

                <!-- LOGO HEADER -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-bottom: 32px; text-align: center;">
                        <!-- Note: Replace this with your actual logo image for production -->
                        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="margin: 0 auto;">
                            <tr>
                                <td style="background-color: #fafafa; width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
                                    <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #09090b;">&#60;/&#62;</span>
                                </td>
                                <td style="padding-left: 10px;">
                                    <span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #fafafa; letter-spacing: -0.025em;">CodeStage</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- MAIN CARD -->
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #18181b; border: 1px solid #27272a; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;">

                            <!-- PURPLE ACCENT BAR -->
                            <!-- Note: Adds visual interest and brand identity -->
                            <tr>
                                <td style="height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7c3aed 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #a78bfa 100%);"></td>
                            </tr>

                            <!-- CARD CONTENT -->
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding: 40px 36px;">

                                    <!-- GREETING SECTION -->
                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #71717a; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Assessment Invitation</p>
                                    <h1 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #fafafa; line-height: 1.3;">
                                        Hi {{candidateName}},
                                    </h1>

                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #a1a1aa; line-height: 1.7;">
                                        You've been invited to complete a coding assessment on CodeStage. This is your opportunity to demonstrate your technical skills in a real-time collaborative environment.
                                    </p>

                                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="background-color: #27272a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px;">
                                                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td style="width: 40px; vertical-align: middle;">
                                                            <div style="width: 36px; height: 36px; background-color: #3f3f46; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 36px;">
                                                                <span style="color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">{{inviterInitials}}</span>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </td>
                                                        <td style="padding-left: 14px; vertical-align: middle;">
                                                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #71717a;">Invited by</p>
                                                            <p style="margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 15px; color: #fafafa; font-weight: 500;">{{inviterName}}</p>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                </table>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>

                                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td align="center">
                                                <a href="{{assessmentLink}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #fafafa; color: #09090b; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; transition: background-color 0.2s;">
                                                    Start Assessment →
                                                </a>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>

                                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="background-color: #27272a; border-left: 3px solid #7c3aed; border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px 20px;">
                                                <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #7c3aed; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
                                                    📝 Additional Instructions
                                                </p>
                                                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #d4d4d8; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{assessmentNotes}}</div>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>

                                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="background-color: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px;">
                                                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td style="width: 24px; vertical-align: top; padding-top: 2px;">
                                                            <span style="font-size: 16px;">⏱️</span>
                                                        </td>
                                                        <td style="padding-left: 12px;">
                                                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #fbbf24; font-weight: 600;">Link expires in 10 minutes</p>
                                                            <p style="margin: 6px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #a1a1aa; line-height: 1.5;">
                                                                This invitation link is time-sensitive for security purposes. Please start your assessment promptly.
                                                            </p>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                </table>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>

                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>


                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-top: 32px; text-align: center;">
                        <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #52525b;">
                            Need help? Contact our support team.
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #3f3f46;">
                            © 2025 CodeStage. All rights reserved.
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>


</body>
</html>